FADAKA CRYPTO CORE PCB SCHEMATIC
=================================

POWER:
- USB-C 5V input
- LiPo battery input (optional)
- Voltage regulator 3.3V

MCU:
- ESP32-WROOM-32

SECURITY:
- ATECC608A secure element (I2C)

STORAGE:
- SPI Flash (or internal ESP32 SPIFFS)

OUTPUT:
- WS2812 LED ring (GPIO control)

COMMUNICATION:
- WiFi (ESP32 internal)
- USB serial debugging
